{"tid":703314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"交上朋友了！ 侵稱週日要打電話給金正恩","createTime":"2018-06-15T15:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T10:04:33.000Z","uid":13663,"like":220,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"f10641d4bf6b2e02293e640ec6333291768950bb","tid":703314,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"交上朋友了！ 川普稱週日要打電話給金正恩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018-06-15 23:18中央社 華盛頓15日綜合外電報導<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/26xBOVNvTYppStULC/giphy.gif \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F26xBOVNvTYppStULC%2Fgiphy.gif%20&h=ed2003bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統川普。 美聯社<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普今天表示，他計畫在17日打電話給北韓領導人金正恩。他們兩人本週剛在新加坡開過高峰會。<br />\n川普在福斯新聞頻道（Fox News）記者詢問他父親節有何計畫時說：「事實上我要打電話到北韓。」<br />\n<br />\n川普在白宮草坪舉行的臨時記者會上並告訴記者，他曾交給金正恩一個電話號碼，以便金正恩能直接連絡他。<br />\n<br />\n川普說：「如果金正恩碰到任何難題，他已經可以打電話給我了，我也可以打給他。」<br />\n<br />\n記者問到川普為金正恩的人權紀錄辯護一事，川普說，「原因你也知道，我不希望看到你和你的家人被核子武器摧毀．．．我希望與北韓保持友好關係」。"},{"pid":"eae580b1cab218eba000bfd26f2a98106890cea7","tid":703314,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8641e49b3fd61c6ded45c77bccc8b7cdb9cd766","tid":703314,"uid":121146,"like":113,"dislike":1,"score":112,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:46:25.000Z","msg":"已收做靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d09995ad4e13831f930edcce2bcc81a7eee0a4","tid":703314,"uid":32722,"like":129,"dislike":3,"score":126,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:49:34.000Z","msg":"中國仲好意思話金仔係佢條𡃁麻？"},{"pid":"e1a90dcd9f80a4d44e551673af44485c57f3c9bc","tid":703314,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f88e269ed532082f2ebec804d45524dde86f75","tid":703314,"uid":157362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:58:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d6d93b048d50413cad6d3cc951214c3b1e6b4ec","tid":703314,"uid":13663,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:03:59.000Z","msg":"特朗普父親節有何活動？ 跟金正恩通電話<br />\n 國際 22:06 2018/06/15  <br />\n    <br />\n<br />\n周日將是父親節，美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）受訪時透露，打算在父親節跟北韓領袖金正恩通電話。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普接受霍士新聞訪問，談及父親節有何活動時，他稱將會向北韓打電話。<br />\n<br />\n現年72歲的特朗普周二跟34歲的金正恩舉行美朝峰會，特朗普會後自言跟金正恩建立了良好關係。<br />\n<br />\n撰文 : 陳啟賢"},{"pid":"0af2bbeb3b89aac1baba40a04a34f06a9e1a9c34","tid":703314,"uid":49853,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:08:11.000Z","msg":"收左做契仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd6335e35c40d3d4ab66417a1e4fb0c05ab136d","tid":703314,"uid":20867,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:13:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 我不希望看到你和你的家人被核子武器摧毀</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想個記者點接落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1e3d219d4870de160c98365d803a7ece2c5e5a","tid":703314,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:47:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc1c4f7cd96bd9d4b1b90b9e204285dabb7893a","tid":703314,"uid":48083,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:48:35.000Z","msg":"侵：好掛住你個肥白大pat pat<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b20c55e2b469fff49a204cb60832666f97d6e5","tid":703314,"uid":121146,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"quote":{"pid":"8cd6335e35c40d3d4ab66417a1e