\n2018-06-15 23:18中央社 華盛頓15日綜合外電報導<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/26xBOVNvTYppStULC/giphy.gif \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F26xBOVNvTYppStULC%2Fgiphy.gif%20&h=ed2003bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統川普。 美聯社<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普今天表示，他計畫在17日打電話給北韓領導人金正恩。他們兩人本週剛在新加坡開過高峰會。<br />\n川普在福斯新聞頻道（Fox News）記者詢問他父親節有何計畫時說：「事實上我要打電話到北韓。」<br />\n<br />\n川普在白宮草坪舉行的臨時記者會上並告訴記者，他曾交給金正恩一個電話號碼，以便金正恩能直接連絡他。<br />\n<br />\n川普說：「如果金正恩碰到任何難題，他已經可以打電話給我了，我也可以打給他。」<br />\n<br />\n記者問到川普為金正恩的人權紀錄辯護一事，川普說，「原因你也知道，我不希望看到你和你的家人被核子武器摧毀．．．我希望與北韓保持友好關係」。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T17:28:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:57:01.000Z","msg":"咁當年支那志願軍做嗰啲算咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738e573fb53d5ff4cbb0dbe980af837b8fea9116","tid":703314,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:12:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8daf647af17d2f0a04bced2eb2e6124982a61ecb","tid":703314,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:12:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8f0d9b8cdd068ee34536b4aa08750b43f4edba2","tid":703314,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:23:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d71ae06bee40c1ad4e565c16068283f76a7c81c","tid":703314,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:23:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0cce17a04394fe10a1acf7c648e0e8b0532002d","tid":703314,"uid":67407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"36f9d7af8ffafc1c6dc9882cb717e8005898d5d8","tid":703314,"uid":162268,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T03:34:22.000Z","msg":"個五毛係咁話北韓點點點<br />\n支那咪殺得仲多人<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><